<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Climate Solutions</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
  </head>
  <!-- welcome part -->
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="hero bg-base-200 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 mb-10">
        <div class="hero-content text-center">
          <div class="max-w-md">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Welcome</h1>
            <p class="py-6">
              Browse our current collection of modern solutions to help fight
              Climate Change.
            </p>
            <a href="/solutions/projects" class="btn btn-primary"
              >Get Started Now</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- grid thing -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- card part 1 -->
        <div class="card bg-base-200 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/solution_farmlandrestoration01.jpg" alt="Abandoned Farmland Restoration" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title">Abandoned Farmland Restoration</h2>
            <p>Restoration can bring degraded farmland back into productivity and sequester carbon in the process.</p>
            <div class="card-actions justify-end">
              <a href="/solutions/projects/1" class="btn btn-primary"
                >More Information</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- card part 2 -->
        <div class="card bg-base-200 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_alternativecement02.jpg" alt="Alternative Cement" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title">Alternative Cement</h2>
            <p>Conventional cement production is a significant source of carbon dioxide. Reformulation can reduce emissions by millions of metric tons each year.</p>
            <div class="card-actions justify-end">
              <a href="/solutions/projects/2" class="btn btn-primary"
                >More Information</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- card part 3 -->
        <div class="card bg-base-200 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_bicycle_infrastructure.jpg" alt="Bicycle Infrastructure" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title">Bicycle Infrastructure</h2>
            <p>Infrastructure is essential for supporting safe and abundant bicycle use, which curbs emissions by reducing the need for fossil-fuel-dependent transportation.</p>
            <div class="card-actions justify-end">
              <a href="/solutions/projects/3" class="btn btn-primary"
                >More Information</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
